profile:
Award Winning Specialists!
416-236-8721

A&A Masonry is an award-winning Toronto based firm specializing in almost everything exterior.  Specialties include Stone work, Interlock, Interlocking, Paver stones, paving stones, Natural Stone, Pavers, Stone Veneer Cladding, Tuckpointing, Masonry, brick repair, brick restoration, tuck pointing, waterproofing, foundation repairs, concrete steps, porches, walkways, caulking services (windows & doors), chimney repair and general exterior restorations for residential, commercial and industrial customers.

A&A is dedicated to providing the highest quality on every job. With a proud team of qualified artisans, we strive to complete every project in a timely and safe manner.

Our mission is to offer a unique and reliable service in anything Exterior within the Greater Toronto Area, differentiating ourselves from the competition by means of always delivering what we promise, on time and on budget.

Our commitment to excellence is our core value.
Customer satisfaction is our main goal, and we reach it every day by relying on our attention to customer service. By providing customized solutions for every job, we guarantee that we will never compromise on quality, safety and efficiency.

This approach together with our experience and knowledge allows us to effectively handle a wide variety of projects, from small to big, indoors or outdoors, renovations or repairs. 

We service:  Toronto, Etobicoke, Mississauga, Thornhill, Richmond Hill, York, North York, East York, Mimico, Hamilton, Brampton, Bolton and surrounding areas. 

For FREE ESTIMATE CALL: 416-236-8721

Being Masonry Contractors, Concrete Contractors, Stone  Contractors & Waterproofing Contractors we specialize in:
Stone work, Interlocking Natural Stone & Pavers, Stone Veneer Cladding, Tuckpointing, Tuck Pointing, Chimney Repair, Chimney Rebuild, Chimney Restoration, tuckpointing, Brickwork, Brick Repair, Brick Replacement, Parging, Waterproofing, Foundation Repair, Concrete Resurfacing, Concrete Porches, Concrete Steps, Patios and Walkways, Flagstone, Cultured Stone, Caulking services (windows and doors), Masonry, Masonry repair, steps, concrete porches, concrete walkways and patios, caulking services.

profile: Aquamaster Group has two divisions to serve you better: Concrete Division that specializes on all types of concrete work like : foundations, underpinnings, additions, concrete walkways, driveways, pads e.c. and Plumbing Division, providing plumbing and drain services, drain cleaning and repair and all associated works as well as waterproofing.  Having two locations, one in Toronto another one in Mississauga gives us possibility to cover sufficient service area and provide you with same day service. We are fully licensed and insured. We guarantee fast and cost efficient solutions and excellent quality services. Knowledge and experience of our workers extends to every area of plumbing, drain, underpinning and waterproofing. We offer emergency plumbing services 24 hours a day, 7 days a week. At Aquamaster we guarantee excellent quality services, individual approach and the most affordable prices in Toronto and GTA. For more than 10 years we have been earning trust from our clients, building superior reputation and becoming most trusted waterproofing company in Toronto and GTA.

profile:
Reinforced Concrete appeals to homeowners, business owners, general contractors, property managers, and even church groups because the RC team understands their specialized needs and has a track record in solutions specific to individual client and job needs.
***
CUSTOMER CONFIDENCE
***
Customers feel comfortable and confident with Reinforced Concrete, who gives them the feel of having an ally and friend helping them to solve problems and to create beauty for their everyday. RC always leaves a footprint that is clean and well organized. Core values of integrity, self- responsibility, and clear communication show up throughout the company.
***
RC seeks input from employees to create an inspiring working environment that emphasizes competence, care, professional growth, and above all-customer satisfaction.
***
LEADING THE MARKET
***
RC continually implements systems to be at the leading edge of their market, specifically in personnel and project management. From the customers’ initial call to the resealing of the project two years latter; from the office to the field the same responsive, caring, competent, attentive, and professional engagement is maintained throughout. We employ those who are friendly, responsive, and efficient, working hard to work together to create ongoing solutions to complete the task at hand.
services: Driveways, walkways, stairs, pads, and much more! This includes special finishes such as: Exposed aggregate, stamping, dyed concrete, and broom finishes.

profile: Ontario Concrete Raising are the concrete raising experts specializing in a process commonly known as slabjacking, mudjacking, slablifting and concrete jacking. Family owned and operated, we have built value in serving our clients as such, bringing peace of mind to every project we undertake. We are accredited by the Better Business Bureau and always strive for excellence in customer satisfaction and workmanship. All residential projects are covered by a 5 Year Warranty which comes detailed in every quotation form. We take pride in every phase of our specialized approach, from our detailed assessment to the completion of your project. We help you protect your investment with our many years of experience and dedication to your project and conduct our business based on the guiding principles of honesty, integrity, and transparency.

profile:
We make your home dream be a reality

At Wise Guys, we are trained to know what customers desire and suit their needs. We take pride in pouring our concrete at a maximum 4 inch slump. That means our workers earn their money by working hard to create leveled surfaces without the concrete being so wet that it is self leveling. We don’t believe in cutting corners.
